                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 812.00/14616.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Governor of Texas</gloss>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-03-18">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 18, 1915</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>General Ricaut, Nuevo Laredo, requests permission to transport over Texas
                    territory wounded soldiers to Matamoros. Please telegraph whether the State of
                    Texas agrees to their transportation over Texas soil from Nuevo Laredo.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">W. J. Bryan.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
